                        <interp inst="t18480515-name-1188" type="given" value="GEORGE"></interp>GEORGE RICHARDS.</persName>
                  </hi> I was at Greenwich fair on Easter Sunday. I saw the prosecutor turn and accuse the prisoner of stealing his watch—the prisoner denied it, and tried to back away from him—the policeman caught him by the collar, and the prisoner dropped the watch.</p>
