               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> He first said he saw me drop the watch, and when the Magis<lb></lb>trate asked him if he were watching my hands he said no. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> I said I saw it fall from his hand—the Magistrate said, "Did you see his hand?"—I said, "No, but it could not come from any one else"—there was no crowd just at that moment—it fell on your left side.</p>
